OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsunny into the evening, with clear
OL,7,Fspells overnight, cloud increasing
OL,8,Ffrom the west towards dawn. Much
OL,9,Fcooler than recent nights. Rather
OL,10,Fbreezy at first, but winds easing
OL,11,Fovernight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FRather cloudy with some bright
OL,14,For sunny spells particularly across
OL,15,FCheshire and Lancashire during the
OL,16,Fmorning. Temperatures close to the
OL,17,Flate June average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
